    "text": "PHEMCE Advisory Committee Act of 2023\n\nThis bill establishes an advisory committee for the\u00a0Public Health Emergency Medical Countermeasures Enterprise (PHEMCE). (The PHEMCE identifies national health security needs and recommends related countermeasures and strategies to address those needs.)\n\nThe committee must support the\u00a0PHEMCE\u00a0by soliciting stakeholder input, coordinating with other government entities, helping to communicate decisions, and generally providing advice regarding the\u00a0PHEMCE's\u00a0duties.\n\n\u00a0"
